module- to import libraries (root module-app module)
component-to create view{html,css,ts}-(root component-app component)
data binding-share data inside component
one way binding-  data sharing only in one direction at a time
   1.component (ts) to view (html)
      string interpolation - {{expression}}
      property bindind - [attribute name]="property name"
   2.view(html) to component(ts)
      event binding - (event-name)="function name()"
      event binding using $event - (event-name)="function name($event)"
      using Template referencing variable - #variable-name